Short description:
Seller: RibbonAndClay
Looking for a gift for a family? Buy them this personalised snowmen ornament for their Christmas tree. Up to 5 snowmen, let me know how many snowmen you'd like in the personalisation box.

A great gift for families this is a fine white porcelain ornament with shiny glaze.

Approx. 70mm across. Comes with white ribbon as standard in a kraft purpose made box ready for gifting.

Personalisation of the front is included in the base price, adding text to reverse side is optional, leave your personalisation in the box provided. Suggested text:

Name, Name, Name & Name


Optional reverse side:
Our first white Christmas
Date

or

Happy Holidays
Love Name etc


Allow 2-3 days for production plus shipping time

Shipping is from Adelaide, Australia
